# Novolis git remotes

Repos under `d:\novolis\*` are **Novolis-Platform** org repositories, not personal forks.

Before `git push`, `git remote add origin`, or `gh repo create`:

1. Run `git remote -v`.
2. `origin` must be `https://github.com/Novolis-Platform/<repo>.git`.
3. For new repos: `gh repo create <name> --org Novolis-Platform` (never omit `--org`).
4. Do not push implementation work to `frankhaugen/novolis-*` remotes.
